<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class-"skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div 
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>              
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I am a fresh graduate from high school and most of my highschool years have been devoted to coding, I have loved it
        ever since I was introduced to it. It is a world of my creation, all I need are the learnable skills, a computer, 
        and lastly an internet connecion. It is almost pure magic. My skills are conveyed in this portfolio, I hope my work
        contains no imperfections.</p>
    
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>